Some believe that the "pinch" action mimics the teeth of a mother dog grabbing a puppy's neck during a correction.You may know that pinch collars can be of different sizes. The size depends not only on the collar's length that, but also from the diameter of the prongs. This prong collar is 22 inch (55 cm) long with prong's diameter - 1/9 inch (3 mm), and consists of 9 links. NOTE!It should be worn high on the dog's neck, right under dog's chin and behind his ears.
